SEARCH
Package util

Class Sort

java.lang.Object
util.Sort
public class Sort extends Object
Provides various sorting functionalities for lists of providers, appointments, and patients. This class contains static methods to sort objects by different criteria.
Author:
Raashi Maheshwari, Tanvi Yamarty
